Class Axis.TickMark<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.chart.Axis.TickMark<T>
  • Enclosing class:
    Axis<T>
    public static final class Axis.TickMark<T>
extends Object
    TickMark represents the label text, its associated properties for each tick along the Axis.
